-- Polish Tour Bus Crash Near Berlin Kills at Least 11 People, N-TV Reports
-- B y   N i c h o l a s   C o m f o r t
-- 2010-09-26T11:47:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-26/polish-tour-bus-crash-near-berlin-kills-at-least-11-people-n-tv-reports.html
At least 11 people have died and
several others are seriously injured after a Polish tour bus
crashed near Berlin,  N-TV  reported, citing unidentified police
officials.  The bus, with 47 people aboard, ran into a pillar, the
German television station reported on its website today without
specifying when the accident occurred.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Nicholas Comfort  in Frankfurt at 
